<div class="sign-up">
  <div class="splash">
    <h1 class="splash-head">jwlr.com</h1>
    <p class="splash-subtitle">
      A social marketplace.
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= link_to "Get Started", signup_url, class: 'pure-button pure-button-primary' %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<h1 class="content-header">Buy and sell jewelry.</h1>
        <div class="pad-box pure-g">
            <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">

                <h3>
                    Product at your fingertips
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Online inventories available to you -- detailed with images, geolocating, and detailed product descriptions. Feel free to message the seller or initiate the purchasing process. 
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3>
                    Built for vendors
                </h3>
                <p>
                  Produce your own virtual storefront, on 24/7, to permanently engage customers.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3>
                    Be social
                </h3>
                <p>
                  Like your new bracelet? Want that necklace? Share it with your friends!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3>
                    Operate effectively
                </h3>
                <p>
		  Bring your business to the next level with jwlr's advanced business tools, like promoted products, inventory, and high-grade customer targeting software.
                </p>  
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ribbon pad-box pure-g">
        <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-3 pure-u-lg-1-5">
          <p class="no-fees">
            $0.00
          </p>
          <p class="no-fees-subheader">
            per item
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-2-3 pure-u-lg-4-5">

            <h1 class="content-header">FREE - no entry fees</h1>

            <p class="no-fees-text">
	      Join a social marketplace where you can share and view content, follow and message other users, post your own product, search for product that matches your interests, engage in deals, create a virtual storefront, engage with customers or vendors, and acquire a great rating in an excellent community.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="content-header">Take a tour.</h1>
        <div class="pad-box pure-g">
            <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">

                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    Featured products
                </h3>
                <p>
                    <% @featured.each do |product| %>
                      <%= render product %>
                    <% end %>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    Featured stores
                </h3>
                <p>
                    <% @featured.each do |product| %>
                      <%= render product %>
                    <% end %>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pad-box pure-g">
            <div class="pure-u-1">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    Most popular
                </h3>
                    <% @top_products.each do |product| %>
                      <%= render product %>
                    <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
